downstairs in the hospital.

907
00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:52,860
They sell them. I'll take you.

908
00:37:53,570 --> 00:37:53,960
Okay?

909
00:37:54,250 --> 00:37:55,530
Shen,

910
00:37:56,170 --> 00:37:57,800
