911
00:37:59,010 --> 00:37:59,790
We'll be right back.

912
00:38:00,010 --> 00:38:00,760
Thank you.

913
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:03,090
Oh, and I'll just leave these here.

914
00:38:03,090 --> 00:38:03,840
Yes.

915
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:05,520
Have a good chat.

916
00:38:05,610 --> 00:38:06,320
You two talk.

917
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:16,280
Why is Ms. Nie

918
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:18,690
being so cold to Professor Shen?

919
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,320
Peng Yulan, I think you...

920
00:38:22,730 --> 00:38:23,690
Who could be happy

