00:38:24,170 --> 00:38:25,760
after being diagnosed with cancer?

922
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:27,250
Jingmin,

923
00:38:27,730 --> 00:38:28,360
my late in-law,

924
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:30,760
didn't speak a word for days

925
00:38:32,050 --> 00:38:33,840
after learning about her metastasis.

926
00:38:35,730 --> 00:38:36,800
And then?

927
00:38:38,250 --> 00:38:39,130
Then,

928
00:38:40,090 --> 00:38:41,800
she couldn't stop talking.

929
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:43,280
Like

930
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:44,920
she had to get

931
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,760
a whole lifetime's worth of words
out at once.

932
00:38:48,730 --> 00:38:49,210
Wang.

933
00:38:49,870 --> 00:38:51,089
You washed the towels already?

934
00:38:51,090 --> 00:38:51,760
I'm fast.

935
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:53,760
No hurry.

936
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,090
Ms. Nie's not in the best mood.

937
