Let her friend try and talk to her.

938
00:38:58,760 --> 00:38:59,530
She needs it.

939
00:39:00,050 --> 00:39:01,730
Ms. Nie is quiet and reserved.

940
00:39:02,250 --> 00:39:02,570
True.

941
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:03,610
Oh,

942
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:06,360
