943
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:08,170
Ms. Nie's appetite is small.

944
00:39:08,530 --> 00:39:09,360
It's only this big.

945
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:11,920
Wang,

946
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:14,360
you can share

