949
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:20,480
I'm not really into those light broths.

950
00:39:21,130 --> 00:39:22,130
I like spicy pepper soup.

951
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,670
That stuff's got punch.

952
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:27,920
Wang, you sure speak your mind.

953
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,480
Yes.

954
00:39:29,250 --> 00:39:30,480
You have to.

955
00:39:30,530 --> 00:39:32,880
In our line of work,
